---
title: Spicy Tex-Mex Turkey Burrito Bowls  with Fajita Veggies, Rice & Lime Crema
description: These turkey burrito bowls are as zesty and fiery as your favorite takeout version. For this 30-minute dish, you’ll sauté ground turkey with fajita veggies and Tex-Mex spices, then serve it over a bed of fluffy jasmine rice topped with creamy, tangy lime crema and a sprinkle of melty Monterey Jack. Just serve with a squeeze of lime, and you’re set!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/671699ba1d41414127643c0c-30e3f16a.jpeg
